    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I think that this would be a nice feature to have in the game client (in EXTRAS).\r\n\r\nAnd if (thanks to the forum login integration) it becomes possible to add these stats on the forum: \r\n- Total Time Played: 06h 53m 24s\r\n- Multiplayer games played: 36\r\n- Wins: 24\r\n- Losses: 12\r\n\r\n... then it would be nice. \r\nThese stats could be displayed on the forum, in the user information DIV (in the class=\"postprofile\" in the CSS)).\r\n\r\n![forum_userstats](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1732773/55276900-ce1f4180-52f9-11e9-8f54-ddd3c789428c.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n"
